snippet.title: Abyssals | REVEAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Abyssals is a Survival City Builder, set in the dark depths of an inhospitable planet. Build your underwater colony, explore the darkest depths of the oceanic planet, and hunt for scarce resources. Expand your infrastructure and power your lamps, as danger lies in the deep, hidden in the dark.

Wishlist Abyssals on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1993210/Abyssals/
